56
00:04:24,874 --> 00:04:25,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi.</b></font>

57
00:04:27,184 --> 00:04:28,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yo, Takumi.</b></font>

58
00:04:28,764 --> 00:04:29,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's up?</b></font>

59
00:04:29,914 --> 00:04:33,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hi, Iketani, and you too, Kenji.</b></font>

60
00:04:33,344 --> 00:04:37,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel sorry for you,
since it's still hot at night.</b></font>

61
00:04:37,264 --> 00:04:40,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, don't treat me like Kenji.</b></font>

62
00:04:40,234 --> 00:04:43,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm working, but he's just goofing off.</b></font>

63
00:04:43,864 --> 00:04:45,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's with you?</b></font>

64
00:04:45,044 --> 00:04:47,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can't you put it a little differently, Iketani?</b></font>

65
00:04:47,764 --> 00:04:49,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right.</b></font>

66
00:04:49,054 --> 00:04:52,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kenji has no date to spend time with.</b></font>

67
00:04:52,754 --> 00:04:53,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shut up!</b></font>

68
00:04:54,454 --> 00:04:58,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Street racers don't need girls!</b></font>

69
00:04:59,064 --> 00:05:01,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How many times have I said that?</b></font>

70
00:05:03,514 --> 00:05:08,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, when will your Eight-Six be ready?
You're doing more mods again, aren't you?</b></font>

71
00:05:08,824 --> 00:05:13,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This time, the main issue is the suspension, and the tire size is being changed, too.</b></font>

72
00:05:14,764 --> 00:05:17,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And strengthening the chassis
plus the reduction of weight.</b></font>

73
00:05:17,464 --> 00:05:21,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're leaving the looks completely unchanged, but modding what's inside, huh?</b></font>

74
00:05:21,664 --> 00:05:24,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder what kind
of car it's going to be?</b></font>

75
00:05:26,614 --> 00:05:29,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's awesome?
Totally awesome?</b></font>

76
00:05:29,534 --> 00:05:35,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After all, you are Project D's undefeated downhill ace, with an uninterrupted series of victories.</b></font>

77
00:05:36,654 --> 00:05:38,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, that's right, Takumi.</b></font>

78
00:05:38,724 --> 00:05:46,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you go on trips with Takahashi Keisuke,
other than Project D's expeditionary races?</b></font>

79
00:05:46,044 --> 00:05:47,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?</b></font>

80
00:05:47,264 --> 00:05:49,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um, no, I don't.</b></font>

81
00:05:49,604 --> 00:05:52,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What made you ask that, Kenji?</b></font>

82
00:05:52,844 --> 00:06:04,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A friend of my friend apparently raved about meeting Project D's double aces last weekend, on a mountain pass in Saitama.</b></font>

83
00:06:04,044 --> 00:06:05,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

84
00:06:05,014 --> 00:06:07,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I never went somewhere like that.</b></font>

85
00:06:07,004 --> 00:06:08,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought so.</b></font>

86
00:06:08,344 --> 00:06:10,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It didn't sound right.</b></font>

87
00:06:10,414 --> 00:06:12,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then what the heck's going on?</b></font>

88
00:06:12,794 --> 00:06:14,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mistaken for someone else?</b></font>

89
00:06:19,214 --> 00:06:20,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Higashi-Chichibu</b></font>

90
00:06:24,514 --> 00:06:25,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Heel and toe!</b></font>

91
00:06:27,364 --> 00:06:28,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How was that, Takumi?</b></font>

92
00:06:28,964 --> 00:06:33,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Someday, I'll emerge as
a downhiller with my Levin.</b></font>

93
00:06:33,714 --> 00:06:35,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's my dream.</b></font>

94
00:06:35,664 --> 00:06:37,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Reality is harsh.</b></font>

95
00:06:38,064 --> 00:06:39,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

96
00:06:39,314 --> 00:06:41,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you mean?</b></font>

97
00:06:41,104 --> 00:06:43,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not talking about you.</b></font>

98
00:06:43,614 --> 00:06:48,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You know I drive around town for
deliveries during the daytime, right?</b></font>

99
00:06:48,644 --> 00:06:53,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I see middle and high school kids
having fun, that thought pops into my head.</b></font>

100
00:06:54,764 --> 00:06:56,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Uh huh.</b></font>

101
00:06:56,264 --> 00:07:00,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've come to think that
summer break is incredible.</b></font>

102
00:07:00,164 --> 00:07:03,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can play around every day.</b></font>

103
00:07:03,334 --> 00:07:06,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now that I've got a job,
I feel such a stark difference.</b></font>

104
00:07:06,614 --> 00:07:08,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see.</b></font>

105
00:07:08,274 --> 00:07:11,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We had summer break last year.</b></font>

106
00:07:11,304 --> 00:07:13,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One year makes a huge difference, doesn't it?</b></font>

107
00:07:13,874 --> 00:07:18,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It makes me sad to think that we'll never have
such a summer break again for the rest of our lives.</b></font>

108
00:07:22,264 --> 00:07:25,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, do you miss...</b></font>

109
00:07:26,974 --> 00:07:28,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Natsuki?</b></font>

110
00:07:34,264 --> 00:07:36,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The reason I said
I have to stay here...</b></font>

111
00:07:39,014 --> 00:07:44,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is because I want to join
a new team and learn a lot.</b></font>

112
00:07:44,454 --> 00:07:49,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think that will bring
me closer to my dream.</b></font>

113
00:07:50,914 --> 00:07:53,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You wanted to go to Tokyo, didn't you?</b></font>

114
00:07:53,974 --> 00:07:57,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then you have to go, no matter what.</b></font>

115
00:07:57,414 --> 00:08:02,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you don't do what you want because
you let a temporary emotion take control</b></font>

116
00:08:02,534 --> 00:08:05,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you'll eventually come 
to regret it in the future.</b></font>

117
00:08:11,874 --> 00:08:16,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I guess I did for
a while, but I'm over it.</b></font>

118
00:08:16,774 --> 00:08:19,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't feel lonely.</b></font>

119
00:08:19,314 --> 00:08:22,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She went to Tokyo to pursue her dream.</b></font>

120
00:08:23,584 --> 00:08:25,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that so?</b></font>

121
00:08:26,184 --> 00:08:30,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm honestly rooting for her
as she chases her dream.</b></font>

122
00:08:34,294 --> 00:08:36,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you come to this mountain pass often?</b></font>

123
00:08:36,754 --> 00:08:38,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is the second time, I guess.</b></font>

124
00:08:38,514 --> 00:08:40,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's boring to only drive on Akina.</b></font>

125
00:08:41,764 --> 00:08:42,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

126
00:08:42,684 --> 00:08:43,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Seriously?!</b></font>

127
00:08:44,064 --> 00:08:45,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder what's going on.</b></font>

128
00:08:45,484 --> 00:08:47,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're getting excited for some reason.</b></font>

129
00:08:47,634 --> 00:08:50,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard Project D's
double aces are coming.</b></font>

130
00:08:50,764 --> 00:08:51,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really?</b></font>

131
00:08:51,434 --> 00:08:52,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Awesome!</b></font>

132
00:08:52,764 --> 00:08:53,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go see</b></font>

133
00:08:53,744 --> 00:08:54,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah</b></font>

134
00:08:55,944 --> 00:08:58,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How could that be possible?</b></font>

135
00:08:58,124 --> 00:08:59,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No idea.</b></font>

136
00:09:08,564 --> 00:09:10,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A panda Trueno and a yellow FD?</b></font>

137
00:09:18,744 --> 00:09:20,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>W-what the?</b></font>

138
00:09:21,264 --> 00:09:23,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>T-shirts with logos</b></font>

139
00:09:23,424 --> 00:09:25,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And dressed the same way?</b></font>

140
00:09:25,164 --> 00:09:26,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never seen anything like that.</b></font>

141
00:09:27,364 --> 00:09:32,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Excuse me, but aren't you 
Takahashi and Fujiwara of Project D?</b></font>

142
00:09:32,644 --> 00:09:34,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hold on.</b></font>

143
00:09:34,324 --> 00:09:39,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry, but I can't answer
yes or no to that question.</b></font>

144
00:09:39,894 --> 00:09:45,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You see, we didn't come
here for an official visit.</b></font>

145
00:09:45,324 --> 00:09:50,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In other words, this is supposed to be a secret, we don't want to create a buzz.</b></font>

146
00:09:50,574 --> 00:09:51,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right, Keisuke?</b></font>

147
00:09:53,194 --> 00:09:56,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's acting so casual with Keisuke.</b></font>

148
00:09:56,244 --> 00:09:58,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Besides, <i>that</i> Keisuke is too short.</b></font>

149
00:09:59,834 --> 00:10:03,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, is it okay for you to let 
them do whatever they want?</b></font>

150
00:10:03,074 --> 00:10:05,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's obvious they're imposters.</b></font>

151
00:10:05,184 --> 00:10:09,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay or not, I don't want to get involved.</b></font>

152
00:10:09,094 --> 00:10:10,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're too embarrassing to watch.</b></font>

153
00:10:11,364 --> 00:10:13,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Excuse me.</b></font>

154
00:10:13,134 --> 00:10:15,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you mind if I take a picture with you?</b></font>

