<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>SLLAAAP, just like that.</b></font>

314
00:19:04,124 --> 00:19:06,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That could be the end.</b></font>

315
00:19:06,184 --> 00:19:09,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think this is over.</b></font>

316
00:19:09,814 --> 00:19:11,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's just a hunch.</b></font>

317
00:19:12,344 --> 00:19:14,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hi, is this Ryosuke?</b></font>

318
00:19:14,084 --> 00:19:15,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's me.</b></font>

319
00:19:15,374 --> 00:19:19,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six is ready, and
I'm going to take it to him.</b></font>

320
00:19:19,504 --> 00:19:20,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

321
00:19:20,454 --> 00:19:23,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was going to call 
you about that matter.</b></font>

322
00:19:23,344 --> 00:19:27,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I found the tag number of the imposter's car.</b></font>

323
00:19:27,294 --> 00:19:29,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh? Already?</b></font>

324
00:19:29,144 --> 00:19:33,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't have the time, so I'll
let Keisuke take care of this.</b></font>

325
00:19:33,534 --> 00:19:41,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I told him not to get too rough, but can you
watch over him while following up on the matter?</b></font>

326
00:19:41,704 --> 00:19:43,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, you can count on me.</b></font>

327
00:19:43,764 --> 00:19:49,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Also, it's a little early, but I'll recon the Kanagawa area with Kenta tomorrow.</b></font>

328
00:19:49,604 --> 00:19:50,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see.</b></font>

329
00:19:50,594 --> 00:19:52,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The time has come.</b></font>

330
00:19:52,694 --> 00:19:58,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Project D is getting closer
to entering its final stage.</b></font>

331
00:19:58,484 --> 00:19:59,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel fulfilled.</b></font>

332
00:20:00,754 --> 00:20:03,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The real challenge begins now.</b></font>

333
00:20:03,144 --> 00:20:06,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll go over courses
more carefully than usual.</b></font>

334
00:20:06,184 --> 00:20:07,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

335
00:20:08,864 --> 00:20:10,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We have one last race in Ibaraki.</b></font>

336
00:20:12,254 --> 00:20:15,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That next hurdle isn't very high.</b></font>

337
00:20:15,624 --> 00:20:19,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Once it's over, Kanagawa, also known as 
the holy ground of street racing, will be next.</b></font>

338
00:20:19,904 --> 00:20:23,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The battles will be unimaginably tough</b></font>

339
00:20:23,264 --> 00:20:29,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but once we overcome the challenge, the true 
meaning of "D" in Project D will become apparent.</b></font>

340
00:20:41,384 --> 00:20:43,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you Mr. Fujiwara of Project D?</b></font>

341
00:20:45,014 --> 00:20:46,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who the hell are you?</b></font>

342
00:20:46,864 --> 00:20:51,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm just a noob.
My name is Akiyama Wataru.</b></font>

343
00:20:52,314 --> 00:20:55,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, chill out.
I just wanna have a friendly talk.</b></font>

344
00:20:55,564 --> 00:20:57,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not picking a fight or anything.</b></font>

345
00:20:58,564 --> 00:21:00,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See?
We're both Eight-Six drivers.</b></font>

346
00:21:05,384 --> 00:21:08,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I, um... how do I put it?</b></font>

347
00:21:08,334 --> 00:21:16,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As an Eight-Six driver, I'm very interested in the driving of the famous Fujiwara Takumi.</b></font>

348
00:21:16,434 --> 00:21:20,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder if you'd show me 
your incredible driving technique.</b></font>

349
00:21:22,564 --> 00:21:25,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, I'm not supposed to do that.</b></font>

350
00:21:25,964 --> 00:21:28,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just one flashy drift, please.</b></font>

351
00:21:29,114 --> 00:21:36,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My request is that you burst out sideways
from the top of that bridge over there, then.</b></font>

352
00:21:36,374 --> 00:21:37,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't.</b></font>

353
00:21:37,484 --> 00:21:39,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke won't allow that.</b></font>

354
00:21:41,824 --> 00:21:48,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The exit is a 90 degree bend, so if you can clear the
corner with only accelerator work, the crowd will go nuts.</b></font>

355
00:21:48,794 --> 00:21:50,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On the line cornering, you see?</b></font>

356
00:21:50,664 --> 00:21:51,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't screw around with me!</b></font>

357
00:21:51,934 --> 00:21:53,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not as easy as you think.</b></font>

358
00:21:53,324 --> 00:21:57,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no such god like driver
who can do it on the first try.</b></font>

359
00:21:57,954 --> 00:21:59,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're right.</b></font>

360
00:21:59,344 --> 00:22:00,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Normally, it's impossible.</b></font>

361
00:22:01,914 --> 00:22:02,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here he comes.</b></font>

362
00:22:03,864 --> 00:22:10,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I guess the world is big, and there's one
moron who can pull it off without any practice.</b></font>

363
00:22:10,264 --> 00:22:11,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Only one.</b></font>

364
00:22:13,124 --> 00:22:14,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Alright, listen guys.</b></font>

365
00:22:16,264 --> 00:22:20,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'd better pay attention and watch what's gonna happen very carefully.</b></font>

366
00:22:21,464 --> 00:22:24,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't get to see it this close very often.</b></font>

367
00:22:25,594 --> 00:22:27,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is real drifting.</b></font>

368
00:22:31,144 --> 00:22:33,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shit, a panda Trueno!</b></font>

369
00:22:37,014 --> 00:22:38,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So fast.</b></font>

370
00:22:38,014 --> 00:22:40,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's much better than before.</b></font>

371
00:22:48,464 --> 00:22:50,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What was that?</b></font>

372
00:22:50,174 --> 00:22:51,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Could it be the real one?</b></font>

373
00:22:52,334 --> 00:22:54,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It must be.</b></font>

374
00:22:54,594 --> 00:22:57,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No other Eight-Six could do that.</b></font>

375
00:22:58,664 --> 00:22:59,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just remembered
some urgent business.</b></font>

376
00:22:59,954 --> 00:23:00,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go, Keisuke.</b></font>

377
00:23:00,944 --> 00:23:01,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

378
00:23:02,724 --> 00:23:03,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What a coincidence.</b></font>

379
00:23:03,994 --> 00:23:05,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your name is Keisuke, huh?</b></font>

380
00:23:08,234 --> 00:23:09,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mine, too.</b></font>

381
00:23:11,574 --> 00:23:13,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's been a while, Wataru.</b></font>

382
00:23:13,354 --> 00:23:15,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, it looks like you're doing alright.</b></font>

383
00:23:21,594 --> 00:23:23,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He was the real!</b></font>

384
00:23:24,054 --> 00:23:26,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now, what should we do with them?</b></font>

385
00:23:26,844 --> 00:23:31,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What gets me most is that
they used Project D's name.</b></font>

386
00:23:32,974 --> 00:23:40,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The team's fame is like a medal of honor.
We managed to build it with the entire team's dedication.</b></font>

387
00:23:41,614 --> 00:23:42,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're sorry!</b></font>

388
00:23:42,604 --> 00:23:43,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please forgive us!</b></font>

389
00:23:45,854 --> 00:23:48,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The second problem</b></font>

390
00:23:48,664 --> 00:23:52,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is that my impostor is so incredibly ugly.</b></font>

391
00:23:52,654 --> 00:23:54,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That deserves a few broken bones.</b></font>

392
00:23:56,604 --> 00:23:58,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry that I'm so ugly.</b></font>

393
00:24:01,674 --> 00:24:02,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Dang.</b></font>

394
00:24:02,354 --> 00:24:03,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just kidding.</b></font>

395
00:24:03,814 --> 00:24:10,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We won't resort to violence or anything,
but make sure you never do this again.</b></font>

396
00:24:10,164 --> 00:24:12,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We can get your name and
address from the tag number.</b></font>

397
00:24:12,724 --> 00:24:15,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't underestimate our information network.</b></font>

398
00:24:15,144 --> 00:24:16,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll never do it again.</b></font>

399
00:24:16,914 --> 00:24:19,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Being in Project D was my dream.</b></font>

400
00:24:21,004 --> 00:24:25,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, Fujiwara, you have something
you wanted to tell them, right?</b></font>

401
00:24:27,814 --> 00:24:28,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um...</b></font>

402
00:24:29,664 --> 00:24:32,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you picked up a girl 
named Tomoko, didn't you?</b></font>

403
00:24:32,464 --> 00:24:35,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I got in trouble because of that.</b></font>

404
00:24:37,674 --> 00:24:43,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Make sure you contact her, and
clear up this misunderstanding</b></font>

405
00:24:43,464 --> 00:24:45,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>since it's been a real pain for me.</b></font>

406
00:24:45,194 --> 00:24:45,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I will!</b></font>

407
00:24:45,864 --> 00:24:46,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I will!</b></font>

408
00:24:46,794 --> 00:24:48,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm very sorry!</b></font>

409
00:24:50,324 --> 00:24:53,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Make sure you do it.</b></font>

410
00:24:53,094 --> 00:24:54,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

411
00:25:01,574 --> 00:25:05,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As you'd expect from a local, he's pretty good for what his car is capable of.</b></font>

412
00:25:08,384 --> 00:25:11,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder how far Project D will go.</b></font>

413
00:25:11,634 --> 00:25:13,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll show them we're out of their league.</b></font>

414
00:25:13,414 --> 00:25:18,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Kanagawa area is known as
the holy ground of street racing.</b></font>

415
00:25:32,914 --> 00:25:36,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Following the brake light of the front car.</b></font>

416
00:25:36,604 --> 00:25:42,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A shimmering light up ahead in the dark street.</b></font>

417
00:25:42,794 --> 00:25:46,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's the silence like a silent film.</b></font>

418
00:25:46,444 --> 00:25:52,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The light was all I could depend on.</b></font>

419
00:25:53,164 --> 00:25:58,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I felt like I could catch it,</b></font>

420
00:25:58,244 --> 00:26:01,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>if I passed through this tree lined street.</b></font>

421
00:26:01,774 --> 00:26:05,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Get up! I just can't understand.</b></font>

422
00:26:05,414 --> 00:26:11,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I couldn't find what I'd been looking for.</b></font>

423
00:26:11,864 --> 00:26:15,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, it starts at this moment.</b></font>

424
00:26:15,354 --> 00:26:19,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At this place.</b></font>

425
00:26:19,024 --> 00:26:22,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please turn over the flyleaf.</b></font>

426
00:26:28,644 --> 00:26:32,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I lost my way.</b></font>

427
00:26:32,254 --> 00:26:35,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fogged up windows, and</b></font>

428
00:26:35,314 --> 00:26:38,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>messed up navigation.</b></font>

429
00:26:38,654 --> 00:26:42,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As the stoplight turns red</b></font>

430
00:26:42,314 --> 00:26:48,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>a light in the side mirror blinds my eyes.</b></font>

431
00:26:48,984 --> 00:26:54,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I gradually close the window</b></font>

432
00:26:54,024 --> 00:26:57,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to stop the cold wind from blowing in.</b></font>

433
00:26:57,454 --> 00:27:01,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Get up! I just can't understand.</b></font>

434
00:27:01,194 --> 00:27:07,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We must choose one of the paths that lie ahead.</b></font>

435
00:27:07,564 --> 00:27:10,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, it starts at this moment.</b></font>

436
00:27:10,984 --> 00:27:14,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Because you're with me.</b></font>

437
00:27:14,604 --> 00:27:17,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please turn over the flyleaf.</b></font>

